---
import Content from '../layouts/Content.astro'
import Heading from '../components/Heading.astro'
import Article from '../components/Article.astro'
---

<style>
  .bee-list {
    list-style-type: none;
  }

  .bee-list li::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-image: url('./pictures/bumblebee2.png');
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    margin-right: 10px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Modern image container with drop shadow */
  .image-container {
    max-width: 350px;
    margin: 1rem auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .image-container {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) 0%,
      rgba(240, 253, 250, 0.95) 100%
    );
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow:
      0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
      0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06),
      0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--ac-primary), 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow:
      0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
      0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05),
      0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .image-wrapper img {
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    width: 100%;
    height: 16rem;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .image-wrapper img {
      height: 20rem;
    }
  }

  /* Improved text readability */
  .content-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-text {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .content-text {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<Content>
  <section>
    <Article>
      <Heading
        slot="header"
        level={1}
        gradient
        class="inline-block"
        text="About me"
        id="about-me"
      />

      <div class="overflow-hidden my-4">
        <!-- First Section: Main Bio -->
        <div class="content-section">
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-center md:items-start"
          >
            <div class="md:col-span-3 order-2 md:order-1">
              <div class="content-text bee-list">
                <p class="mb-4">
                  I am a conservation biologist and research scientist
                  passionate about ecological research. My past work has focused
                  largely on bumble bee conservation, but also includes studies
                  on bumble bee movement, habitat connectivity, and ecosystem
                  restoration.
                </p>

                <p class="mb-4">
                  I now work as a freelance ecological consultant, bringing
                  experience from my previous roles as a Research Scientist at
                  the Toronto and Region Conservation Authority (TRCA),
                  University of Guelph, University of British Columbia, and York
                  University. I offer expertise in statistical analysis, GIS
                  mapping, bee conservation, literature reviews, and more,
                  supporting conservation and biodiversity initiatives across
                  Canada.
                </p>

                <div>
                  <p class="mb-3 font-semibold text-neutral-700">
                    <strong>My research interests are:</strong>
                  </p>
                  <ul class="space-y-2">
                    <li>behavioural ecology</li>
                    <li>conservation</li>
                    <li>restoration</li>
                    <li>pollinators</li>
                    <li>all things bumble bees!</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="mt-6 p-4 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl border border-primary/10"
                >
                  <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-2">
                    Looking to hire an ecologist?
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-3">
                    I'm available for consulting projects across Canada.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a
                      href="/services"
                      class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline transition-colors font-medium"
                      >View Services</a
                    >
                    <span class="text-neutral-400">|</span>
                    <a
                      href="/contact"
                      class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline transition-colors font-medium"
                      >Contact Me</a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-2 order-1 md:order-2">
              <div class="image-container">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                  <img
                    src="/pictures/AmandaLiczner.jpg"
                    alt="Amanda Liczner headshot in the field"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Second Section: Research Techniques -->
        <div class="content-section">
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-center md:items-start"
          >
            <div class="md:col-span-2 order-1">
              <div class="image-container">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                  <img
                    src="/pictures/Bumble.jpg"
                    alt="Bumble bee with a radio tag on dandelions"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-3 order-2">
              <div class="content-text bee-list">
                <p class="mb-4">
                  I have conducted research with a variety of techniques
                  including:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                  <li>field sampling of bees, nests, and plants</li>
                  <li>statistical modelling</li>
                  <li>conservation planning</li>
                  <li>systematic literature reviews</li>
                  <li>radio telemetry to study movement behaviour</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                  You can learn more about the skills I have picked up along the
                  way on my <a
                    href="/skills-education"
                    class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline transition-colors"
                    >skills page</a
                  >.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Third Section: Personal -->
        <div class="content-section">
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-center md:items-start"
          >
            <div class="md:col-span-2 order-1">
              <div class="image-container">
                <div class="image-wrapper">
                  <img
                    src="/pictures/Phoebe.jpg"
                    alt="Amanda Liczner with Phoebe in a kayak"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-3 order-2">
              <div class="content-text">
                <p class="mb-4">
                  Although my specialty is bumble bee research, I am open to
                  working on any ecological research project, especially those
                  with an applied angle. View some of my past research examples
                  on my
                  <a
                    href="/experience"
                    class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 underline transition-colors"
                    >experience page</a
                  >.
                </p>

                <p>
                  When I am not out searching for bumble bees or analyzing data,
                  you can find me hanging out with my dog, gardening, hiking,
                  playing violin, baking or crafting!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Article>
  </section>
</Content>
